snippet.title: Two Strikes - Teaser Trailer - Early Access!
snippet.description:
Wishlist now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1586750/Two_Strikes/


After two and a half years of game development, we are proud to show you the first teaser trailer for Two Strikes, displaying in full HD quality the four initial characters: Kenji, Tomoe, Goemon and Hozoin.
